thread.title: Deadly protests ahead of Israel's 70th Independence Day

title: Deadly protests ahead of Israel's 70th Independence Day
text:
Deadly protests ahead of Israel's 70th Independence Day   01:29 
Several Palestinians were killed and hundreds injured by Israeli security forces confronting one of the largest Palestinian demonstrations along the Israel-Gaza border in recent years, Gaza medical officials said on Friday (March 30). Matthew Larotonda reports.
